---
title: Seared Chicken & Smokey Capsicum Relish with Garlicky Greens & Lemon
description: Bright, bold, and bursting with flavour! This meal pairs juicy, golden chicken with a smokey-sweet relish that takes things up a notch. Served alongside garlicky greens and a zing of fresh lemon, it’s a simple yet sensational dish that’s sure to impress!

*We’ve replaced the green beans in this recipe with courgette due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
